OL,3,C'Extraordinary honour' - new Lord
OL,4,CMayor to make history after 800 years
OL,6,FThe next Lord Mayor of Liverpool is to
OL,7,Fmake history today as the first
OL,8,Fwheelchair user to take up the role.
OL,10,FCllr William Shortall will be
OL,11,Fconfirmed as the city's first citizen
OL,12,Fat a meeting at Liverpool Town Hall
OL,13,Fthis evening.
OL,15,FThe Old Swan Labour member wants to
OL,16,Fuse his year in office to shine a
OL,17,Fspotlight on inclusion and
OL,18,Faccessibility.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
