OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778681476
OL,3,C'Extraordinary honour' - new Lord
OL,4,CMayor to make history after 800 years
OL,6,FHe will take over from incumbent Lord
OL,7,FMayor Cllr Barbara Murray who will
OL,8,Fstep down later today.
OL,10,FBorn and educated in the city, he
OL,11,Fearned his law degree through
OL,12,Fparttime study with The Open
OL,13,FUniversity and the Chester College of
OL,14,FLaw, balancing his community
OL,15,Fvolunteering with life as a wheelchair
OL,16,Fuser with Muscular Dystrophy, a
OL,17,Fprogressive muscle wasting condition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
