CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778681476
OL,3,C'Extraordinary honour' - new Lord
OL,4,CMayor to make history after 800 years
OL,6,FHe said it was an "extraordinary
OL,7,Fhonour" to be invited to serve as the
OL,8,FLord Mayor, the first wheelchair user
OL,9,Fin more than 800 years of history.
OL,11,FCllr Shortall has worked in various
OL,12,Froles from a pub, an electronic
OL,13,Fservicing business and volunteering in
OL,14,Fthe community.
OL,16,FHe has been a councillor since 2019,
OL,17,Frepresenting Old Swan and then Old
OL,18,FSwan West since 2023.
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
