PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778681476
OL,3,C'Extraordinary honour' - new Lord
OL,4,CMayor to make history after 800 years
OL,6,FHe won 67% of the vote during the last
OL,7,Fround of all-out elections for Labour,
OL,8,Fhaving been victorious in a by-
OL,9,Felection four years earlier.
OL,11,FAs chair of Liverpool City Council's
OL,12,FCorporate Access Forum, he leads the
OL,13,Fcity's work to champion accessibility,
OL,14,Fstrengthen inclusive policy, and
OL,15,Fensure disabled residents' voices
OL,16,Fshape decisionmaking.
OL,18,FCllr Shortall's wife Marie will be
OL,19,FLady Mayoress, and his two daughters
OL,20,FMelissa and Laura will share the role
OL,21,Fof consort.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
