OL,3,C'Extraordinary honour' - new Lord
OL,4,CMayor to make history after 800 years
OL,6,FThe Greenbank Project has been chosen
OL,7,Fas the new Lord Mayor's charity and
OL,8,Fthe direct beneficiaries will be
OL,9,FGreenbank College education, training
OL,10,Fand employment services, and Greenbank
OL,11,FSports Academy which delivers sport
OL,12,Fand recreational opportunities.
OL,14,FSpeaking ahead of his ascension to the
OL,15,FTown Hall dais, Cllr Shortall said:
OL,16,F"It is an extraordinary honour to be
OL,17,Finvited to serve as Lord Mayor of
OL,18,FLiverpool.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
