PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778681476
OL,3,C'Extraordinary honour' - new Lord
OL,4,CMayor to make history after 800 years
OL,6,FAs the first wheelchair user to hold
OL,7,Fthis office in our city's 816year
OL,8,Fhistory, I am deeply proud to
OL,9,Frepresent a community that values
OL,10,Finclusion, resilience and opportunity
OL,11,Ffor all.
OL,13,F"My family, friends and colleagues are
OL,14,Fthrilled that I have been entrusted
OL,15,Fwith the role of first citizen of this
OL,16,Fremarkable city.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
