OL,3,C'Extraordinary honour' - new Lord
OL,4,CMayor to make history after 800 years
OL,6,F"They expect me to embody Liverpool's
OL,7,Fhighest values and to extend our
OL,8,Ftraditional warm welcome to everyone
OL,9,Fwho calls this place home, the world
OL,10,Fin one city or comes to share in its
OL,11,Fspirit."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
